<P>
   In response to his recent proclamation that San Francisco is the
No. 1 city in America, challenging Charlotte, N.C., San Francisco
Supervisor  &UR; Mark Leno &LR;  received a letter from City Councilman  &UR; Don
Reid  &LR; of the Charlotte City Council gleefully noting that Charlotte
is HQ of the new NationsBank/BofA.
</P>
<P>
   ``How do you like them apples?'' wrotes Reid. ``The Bridge is
next.''
</P>
<P>
   - The postal service, which often delivers mail, is unveiling
its new  &UR; Alfred Hitchcock &LR;  stamp today at the upscale restaurant
Vertigo, where  &UR; Lester Yee &LR; , U.S. Postal Service marketing manager,
will be introduced, along with a dessert named for the Hitchcock
movie.
