it _ reflect a grand world view, and a peek into the looking glass,
too: Coit's cold cream concoction uses wax, mutton suet and almond
oil.
</P>
<P>
   The book, around $21, is available from the Bancroft Library in
Berkeley.
</P>
<P>
   &LR;   &LR;   &UR; IN THE WHITE HOUSE &LR;
</P>
<P>
   -  &UR; Sidney Blumenthal &LR; , aide to &UR; Bill Clinton &LR; , has framed his
subpoena from  &UR; Kenneth Starr &LR;  and placed it on view in his White
House office, reports the National Journal.
