<P>
   - The postal service, which often delivers mail, is unveiling
its new  &UR; Alfred Hitchcock &LR;  stamp today at the upscale restaurant
Vertigo, where  &UR; Lester Yee &LR; , U.S. Postal Service marketing manager,
will be introduced, along with a dessert named for the Hitchcock
